column3: Is there a changelog for miniupnp? I can't find relevant commits here: https://github.com/miniupnp/miniupnp/commits/miniupnpd_1_9\n

@jonasschnelli the changelog for miniupnpc is [here](http://miniupnp.tuxfamily.org/files/changelog.php?file=miniupnpc-1.9.20160209.tar.gz).\nThe changelogs for all other mini binaries can be found on this page http://miniupnp.tuxfamily.org/files/\n

This would be the approximate diff (approximately, as it's based on dates - miniupnpc doesn't tag releases):\nhttps://github.com/miniupnp/miniupnp/compare/3c18a3ef029ff9acf3b2fb15774ebc7b24e2d1f6...81e0ca10df401e7d188da36f20e118f68ddbd590\n
